<HEADLINE>
FT  24 FEB 94 / World Stock Markets: South Africa
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Industrial stocks fell back slightly on worse than expected inflation data
and the index closed off 8 at 5,689. The overall index slipped 7 to 4,816
and the gold shares index was unchanged at 1,855. SA Breweries lost R1 at
R85.
