</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
Spot and shipment sales in Liverpool amounted to 50 tonnes for the week
ended February 18, against 131 tonnes in the previous week. Restricted
operations involved few fresh dealings. Only occasional interest was
displayed in Mali styles.
